# agent-readiness-kit — environment variables
#
# This CLI runs locally against a repository path. It does not call external
# APIs, store credentials, or require a .env file for normal use.
#
# Copy to .env only if you use these optional overrides in scripts or tooling.

# Optional: override the default repo path when wrapping ark in shell scripts
# ARK_REPO_PATH=.

# Optional: Node.js runtime (e.g. for CI or local dev tooling)
# NODE_ENV=development

# Do not put secrets here. Never commit real API keys, tokens, or production URLs.
